r />\n但因為佢去exchange一個月<br />\n唔知係咪佢太掛住我<br />\n佢開始因為啲細微位發脾氣<br />\n去一個月有2/3時間都嘈緊<br />\n大家都覺得心很累<br />\n之後又再次提出分手<br />\n雖然今次佢搵返我<br />\n話好想一齊落去<br />\n但唔知點解我今次真係覺得心好攰好淡<br />\n我好清楚知我仲愛佢掛住佢<br />\n但係我唔知點行落去<br />\n感覺上之後都係會咁無限輪迴<br />\n段感情已經變咗質<br />\n有冇巴絲明白 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:22:50.000Z","msg":"我同我條女都一9樣<br />\n但我覺得只要雙方仲愛大家<br />\n無出軌無第三者就唔應該咁易放棄<br />\n你今日放棄咗條女<br />\n到下個終於識點對佢好<br />\n你有機會從此失去佢 後悔一世<br />\n唔好聽兒登仔講咩分手仲好<br />\n好多都係抱住食花生心態<br />\n我同條女就係堅持為對方改<br />\n宜家一齊得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a43e75f47e14df96f4f6e116df541184256e264","tid":775174,"uid":171370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5d271638c1e9cd5c27325e50c781b2b980511f3b","tid":775174,"uid":199687,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"a4380eb9a650e3b847957fd59d2533fd8c709286","tid":775174,"uid":78018,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e13c245b985a1782f1e321355b4947c9f50e5ebd","tid":775174,"uid":199687,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T05:48:51.000Z","msg":"呢幾點足夠另大家分開"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:33:21.000Z","msg":"你自己分完手唔好隨便勸人分手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T06:47:14.000Z","msg":"都係想佢早日解脫姐 有錯咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:26:19.000Z","msg":"抵你俾女飛啦"},{"pid":"35b50608b77d1cd528b9c97dac3810c7d2d3d3af","tid":775174,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T07:29:01.000Z","msg":"一齊得咁辛苦， 轉做sp 算啦"},{"pid":"7d8e1d71a5d26efa5a65d10555af763896732a09","tid":775174,"uid":6021,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"92707d269b07280f1f9b6fd9996641604f2c3c2a","tid":775174,"uid":1